<b>What steps will reproduce the problem?</b>
1. Go to the linked test page.
2. Click and drag in the green box &quot;drag area&quot;

<b>What is the expected result?</b>
MOUSE_DOWN, MOUSE_MOVE, and MOUSE_UP events should be logged in the console above.

<b>What happens instead?</b>
Only MOUSE_DOWN and MOUSE_UP events are logged.

